-- 2025.08.05 - v1.1.0

- feat: Moved gamedata to an external file to simplify future updates.
- feat: Automatically disables hooks and commands when no hostages are spawned in a round.
- fix: Updated function signatures to align with the latest CS2 changes.
- fix: Standardized signature names to use fully qualified names for clarity.
- remove: Removed the "Configs enabled" option; if the list is empty, configs are now ignored by default.
